Class ConcreteWall

java.lang.Object
  GameObject.GameObject
      GameObject.StaticObject
          GameObject.ConcreteWall

public class ConcreteWall
extends StaticObject

Used to represent the ConcreteWall objects placed on the grid at fixed positions during GamePlay. Note that this object falls in the category of static objects, and it provides no other logic than the one needed for collision detection.
